            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Valerius Optatus <lb n="2"/>Augustalis <expan><abbr>perp</abbr><ex>etuus</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>huic ordo municipii Flavi <lb n="4"/>Sosontigitanorum <lb n="5"/>cenas publicas decrevit <lb n="6"/>et locum in quo sta<lb break="no" n="7"/>tuas sibi uxori <expan><abbr>liberisq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>poneret loco adsignato <lb n="9"/>ponendas curavit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Das Stück ist heute verschollen. (B): CIL II 1721, ILS 5492: Z. 4: SOSON EGLIANORUM.</p>
            </div>
